metadata.name: Winter Night
metadata.description:
Unusually this winter lasted quite a long time. When winter comes, as usual, there will be a war between the bull cartel and the bear cartel to dominate the market. Almost half of year, winter is not over yet, and neither is this damn war.

This war caused many losses for both parties as well as for the "Whales", especially for civilians who don't understand and had nothing to do with this war. This war caused a long global crisis. Many children have dropped out of school, even many marriages have been forced to cancel due to the crisis. I don't know how many lives have been lost in vain. I don't know when winter will end, I hope this damn war ends as soon as possible.

A few days ago, I got a picture of Pepe and his herd of Bulls are saving Ether by the cartel bear's siege. I don't know what happened, but I hope they can survive the ambush of that cursed cartel bear.
